              ATP2B3
              (G123R) and
              CACNA1D
              (S410L) were discovered in the tumours without known mutations. Adenomas with
              CTNNB1
              mutations showed a large number of differentially expressed genes (1360 compared to 106 and 75 for
              KCNJ5
              and
              ATP1A1
